OL,3,CHalf of UK households struggling to
OL,4,Ccover cost of essentials, Which? warns
OL,6,FHalf of UK households are struggling
OL,7,Fwith the cost of everyday essentials,
OL,8,Fa survey suggests.
OL,10,FThe latest Which? Consumer Insight
OL,11,FTracker found that 49% of households
OL,12,Fare being forced to dip into savings,
OL,13,Fsell possessions or take other
OL,14,Fmeasures to cover the cost of
OL,15,Fessentials.
OL,17,FThe survey found that confidence in
OL,18,Fthe future of the UK economy plummeted
OL,19,Fby 13 points to minus 56 in the month
OL,20,Fto March 13, the lowest level recorded
OL,21,Fsince the end of 2022.
