OL,3,CHalf of UK households struggling to
OL,4,Ccover cost of essentials, Which? warns
OL,6,FThe watchdog said the score reflected
OL,7,F"a deep-seated pessimism across the
OL,8,Fcountry", with 67% of UK adults now
OL,9,Fexpecting the national economy to
OL,10,Fworsen over the next 12 months, while
OL,11,Fjust 12% think it will improve.
OL,13,FIt found that 26% of households now
OL,14,Fregularly dip into savings to bridge
OL,15,Fthe gap between their income and the
OL,16,Frising cost of essentials ` in
OL,17,Fcontrast with the end of 2025 when
OL,18,Ffinancial stress appeared to be
OL,19,Fdeclining.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@HO]
