OL,3,CHalf of UK households struggling to
OL,4,Ccover cost of essentials, Which? warns
OL,6,FConfidence in the future of household
OL,7,Ffinances has also hit its lowest level
OL,8,Fsince April last year, falling five
OL,9,Fpoints to minus 15.
OL,11,FSue Davies, Which? head of consumer
OL,12,Fprotection policy, said: "Our research
OL,13,Fshows a concerning shift in consumer
OL,14,Fsentiment, with confidence in the
OL,15,Feconomy hitting its lowest point in
OL,16,Fyears as households face a daunting
OL,17,Fcombination of rising prices and
OL,18,Fglobal instability.
OL,26,@tD@ZOU
