OL,3,CHalf of UK households struggling to
OL,4,Ccover cost of essentials, Which? warns
OL,6,F"Millions are now being forced to dip
OL,7,Finto savings or sell possessions just
OL,8,Fto keep up with the cost of everyday
OL,9,Fessentials.
OL,11,F"Pressure on budgets is becoming
OL,12,Funsustainable for many. We would
OL,13,Fencourage anyone who is struggling to
OL,14,Fkeep up with their bills to speak to
OL,15,Ftheir providers as soon as possible
OL,16,Fand seek free, independent debt
OL,17,Fadvice."
OL,19,FYonder surveyed 2,085 UK adults
OL,20,Fbetween March 13-15.
